# Prompt Lab

Dev-only sub-application for testing translation prompts in isolation. **Not available when `NODE_ENV=production`.**

## Module map

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/prompt-lab/` | Server: ephemeral runner, Supabase CRUD, API routes |
| `src/prompt-lab-app/` | Preact SPA — workbench UI (`components/`, `panels/`, `styles/`) |
| `src/shared/llmModels.ts` | Shared model list (main app settings + Prompt Lab meta) |
| `supabase/migrations/*_prompt_lab_*.sql` | Supabase tables (`prompt_lab_*`) — see `@.cursor/rules/supabase.mdc` |

## UI components (prompt-lab-app)

| Component | Role |
|-----------|------|
| `PlModal`, `PlSelect`, `PlCollapsible`, `PlDiffView` | Design-system primitives (do not import `src/client/components/ui`) |
| `PlParagraphCompareView` | Side-by-side paragraph compare (Review) |
| `EvaluationResultView` | LLM evaluation score and issues |
| `PromptEditorModal` | Fullscreen system/user prompt editing, diff, save version |
| `WorkbenchPanel` | 3-column workbench (config / prompts / input+result) |
| `ReviewPanel` | Run pickers, compare view, evaluate (header **Review** tab) |

## Meta API shape

`GET /api/prompt-lab/meta` (dev-only): `pairs[]` with `{ source, target, label }`, `models`, `defaultModel`, `analysisExcludedModels`, `stages`, `executionModes` (translate + edit), `defaultChunkSize`, `focusOptions`.

Execution mode architecture and Lab vs prod migration: `docs/03-explanation/prompt-lab-engine-config.md`.

## Boundary

- Does **not** write to `chapters`, `glossary_entries`, or production prompt modules.
- Baseline prompts always loaded from `src/engine/` via `getEffectiveStagePrompts`.
- Saved prompt versions live in `prompt_lab_prompts` only.
- Separate design system in `src/prompt-lab-app/` — do **not** import `src/client/components/ui`.

## Dev workflow

```bash
npm run dev          # API + client + debug + prompt-lab (:5175)
npm run dev:full     # + worker
```

- UI: `http://localhost:5175/prompt-lab/` or via main client proxy `http://localhost:5173/prompt-lab`
- API: `http://localhost:3000/api/prompt-lab/*`

## Supabase

New Prompt Lab schema migrations: `supabase/migrations/YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_prompt_lab_*.sql` only (`@.cursor/rules/supabase.mdc`). Legacy copies may exist under gitignored `docs/migrations/` — do not add new files there.

Typical files (local, under `supabase/migrations/`): `*_prompt_lab_tables.sql` (tables), `*_prompt_lab_review.sql` (`display_name` on runs + `prompt_lab_evaluations`).

Uses `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` server-side (dev-only routes).

## Engine hooks

Stages accept optional `systemPromptOverride` / `userPromptOverride` in options (Prompt Lab only by default).

See `@src/engine/prompts/effective-prompts.ts` for baseline system prompt composition.
